title: So You Think You Can Dance Australia Season 3
description:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia:

Season three of "So You Think You Can Dance Australia", the Australian version of the American reality dance-off series "So You Think You Can Dance", was hosted by former Rogue Traders vocalist and solo artist Natalie Bassingthwaighte, with Jason Coleman, Matt Lee and Bonnie Lythgoe acting as the judges. It premiered on 31 January 2010. Auditions for the third season were held in September and October 2009 in Perth, Brisbane, Melbourne, Adelaide and Sydney
